Package: wordpressr
Type: Package
Title: An API Wrapper for WordPress Site APIs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Simit", "Patel", email = "simit@sixjupiter.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://sixjupiter.com/wordpressr
BugReports: https://github.com/jupitertrades/wordpressr/issues
Description: An API wrapper that helps R developers retrieve data from a WordPress site's API in tidy format, in addition to
    publishing content on the WordPress site. 
